{"tid":354490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（沙士又黎）廣州直通男女染新沙士 晚上抵紅磡後送院","createTime":"2017-08-10T13:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T00:24:39.000Z","uid":56810,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f23083675b106aedacfdd2cd6cdc079cdeea6ff","tid":354490,"uid":56810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"港鐵表示，晚上7時許接獲紅磡站衛生署港口衛生處通知，指一名外籍男子及一名外籍女童於傍晚6時18分，由廣州東/常平站乘坐Z815次城際內地直通車到達紅磡站，在經過紅磡站港口衛生處時，出現發燒及疑似俗稱「新沙士」的中東呼吸綜合症(MERS)的徵狀。該兩名乘客其後被安排乘坐救護車前往醫院作進一步跟進。港鐵會與衛生防護中心保持聯繫。"},{"pid":"f34e75ac79791bc5aee3d42d5dc03e80533af32b","tid":354490,"uid":18569,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:35:11.000Z","msg":"支那真係好撚麻煩"},{"pid":"6a480100a4998d6143a8cffd4d8eb8790d953e84","tid":354490,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"7年到了"},{"pid":"daa706c910e0390f6a9a2592f347b5262cc3d47d","tid":354490,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:35:56.000Z","msg":"人道毀滅啦"},{"pid":"fd6fa34e7d506310c413309351e79d115a695cf0","tid":354490,"uid":41944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"樓價down down down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836b82eab59235c91ffe2f0609c0352b9f72b70c","tid":354490,"uid":26937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"等左好耐"},{"pid":"4f79cc45dda8908c51c7d6918c0c966e5b3ceaca","tid":354490,"uid":114040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21137faf1211d9f1b1ccd0a0c764edaba4f412b8","tid":354490,"uid":131691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:38:09.000Z","msg":"最好中國真係爆發<br />\n死多啲<br />\n樓價物價冧係絕對嘅好事"},{"pid":"f0dc9a08ffc39270b78291b1278ef264265d340d","tid":354490,"uid":122331,"like":12